  "texts": [
    "To understand the contribution of SOB score to the confidence of DEEPOMICS FFPE, we superimposed the SOB score as the confidence of DEEPOMICS FFPE (Supplementary Fig.",
    "The somatic variants confidently predicted were less strand biased (rectangle in Supplementary Fig.",
    "S4B and S4D), whereas the variants classified as artifacts were strand biased (rectangle in Supplementary Fig.",
    "S4A and S4C).",
    "This result indicated that the SOB score provided discriminating power to variant classification in the area where DEEPOMICS FFPE confidently predicted true somatic variants."
